# Coding

- TypeScript, match existing style; no unnecessary abstractions.
- **Tests** (`tests/**/*.spec.ts`): Playwright API only; deterministic assertions; no LLM calls.
- **Library code** (`src/`): pure functions where possible; side effects isolated (e.g. services).
- Prefer explicit file names and one concern per module.
- Reuse helpers under `src/core/` rather than duplicating long selectors in every spec (when introduced).
